  "title": "Technical Service Technician (Night Shift, Up to $2,500 + Allowances)",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Description</strong></u><br />A manufacturing company in Singapore is hiring a full-time Technical Service Technician. You will support production by operating equipment, performing preventive maintenance, and troubleshooting to meet output and quality targets. Training will be provided, fresh graduates are welcome.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong><br />• Operate manufacturing equipment to meet production schedule and output targets<br />• Troubleshoot equipment issues to minimise downtime and meet quality standards<br />• Perform daily and monthly preventive maintenance to improve equipment reliability<br />• Support workplace safety practices and participate in quality improvement projects<br />• Maintain basic records for maintenance activities and equipment performance</p><p><strong>Requirements</strong><br />• Minimum NITEC in an Engineering discipline (Mechanical, Mechatronics, Robotics, or related)<br />• Able to read and understand electrical and mechanical diagrams<br />• Comfortable with 12-hour shift work and willing to work overtime when required<br />• Able to lift and carry 10–15kg<br />• Willing to work in a controlled manufacturing environment<br />• Open to fresh graduates<br />• Eligible to work in Singapore without employer sponsorship</p><p><u><strong>Shift Pattern</strong></u><br />• 12-hour shift, 4-3-3-4 work/rest cycle<br />Week 1: Work 4 days, rest 3 days<br />Week 2: Work 3 days, rest 4 days<br />Repeat cycle<br />• Assigned shift: Sunday Night Shift, 7:45pm to 7:55am</p><p>Salary & Allowances<br />• Basic Salary: Up to $2,500 per Month<br />• Allownaces: Up to $400++ per Month</p><p>Location<br />• Jurong East</p><p>Interested?<br />Kindly WhatsApp 8839 0096 and mention “Technical Service Technician”.</p><p>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Epiphanius Tan<br />Outsourcing Team<br />Crew By HRnet | HRnet Ventures Pte Ltd (24C2435)</p>",
